@Inasyn Probably no to the flavour text, and definitely no to the mathmatically solving. Prismata has way too much state complexity for a computer to exhaustively search everything. Our AI developer thinks it's significantly harder to solve than chess, but some simple subgames are probably solveable.
@xYotsuba I guess we could throttle those server messages, but why are you clicking so much?
@Crash_overlord Not a significant increase, but I was contacted by 2 journalists about it so we'll see... ;)
@Scythius I think I filled your order, if not then I will do so in the next hour or two before bed
