[2018-06-09 07:33] elyot: @wickedcossack You can click out of the queue once you're in a game, we always figure it's better to give people more options than to restrict them.
@ZyphDoz The upgrade to founder's edition is for people who bought the game, we have never given away the $25 version for free.
@Rando We're adding a new welcome splash to the game and we'll be incorporating those kind of aspects.
